Common Market for Eastern and Southern Africa (COMESA) in Nairobi,
Kenya.
</P>
<P>
At the summit which called for intensifying efforts to
eliminate non- tariff barriers and other obstacles to free trade
in the region, Museveni said that economic integration is
essential for the development of Africa and progress in the COMESA
region, a press release from the President's Office said.
</P>
