sector, he said, calling for national and regional support for the
private sectors.
</P>
<P>
He also addressed issues concerning regional security and
stability, the press release said.
</P>
<P>
Museveni, who left for the regional summit Sunday afternoon,
was met by Vice President Specioza Kazibwe and other senior
government officials at the Entebbe International Airport Tuesday
afternoon. 
