published Yearbook On Religion Research 1996 has more than 500,000
Chinese characters and is in three parts: academic papers,
research findings and reference materials.
</P>
<P>
In the yearbook's reference materials section readers can find
introductions to China's major religious research, teaching and
publication institutes, the contents of religious books and
magazines published in 1996 and a list of important events
regarding religious affairs from 1990 to 1996 in China. 
