<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Stocks Close Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, May 26 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks gained 62.25
points, or 0.50 percent, to close at 12,409.16 Wednesday.
