<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 26 (Xinhua) -- Philatelists from 66 countries and
regions will participate in a stamp competition at the event which
takes place between August 21st and 30th, announced the organizing
committee of the China 1999 World Philatelic Exhibition today.
</P>
<P>
"Some 42 stamp experts from 29 countries will select the final
winners of the competition," according to Liu Jiawei, a senior
organizer.
</P>
<P>
