examples from private collectors and valuable stamps from the
collections of a number of major museums," Liu said.
</P>
<P>
The China Philatelic History and China Philatelic Dictionary,
both compiled by the All-China Philatelic Federation will be also
be on show, amongst other items.
</P>
<P>
Liu said that preparations for the exhibition are well advanced.
</P>
<P>
Visitors will be able to view a range of rare Chinese cultural
relics in the exhibition halls. And Liu revealed that already all
the exhibition stands have been booked by worldwide participants.
</P>
<P>
The organizers will also equip the halls in China International
Exhibition Center with high-tech monitoring systems and there will
be round-the-clock security guards keeping an eye on the valuable
exhibits.  
