<HEADLINE> Trading on Hong Kong Stock Exchange </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, May 26 (Xinhua) -- Following are Hang Seng Index
(key
indicator of Hong Kong's blue chips), Hang Seng China Enterprises
Index, Hang Seng China-Affiliated Corporations Index and turnover
