<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Stocks Lower at Midday </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, May 26 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks dropped 38.79
points, or 0.31 percent, to finish the morning session at
12,308.12 Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The key Hang Seng Index dropped 113.85 points, or 0.92 percent,
to open at 12,233.06 Wednesday. 
</P>
