dissatisfaction" over the Philippine navy's ramming of a Chinese
fishing boat in the South China Sea, saying that Huangyan Island
is Chinese territory and the collision of the Philippine navy
vessel with the Chinese fishing boat seriously endangered the
personal safety of the Chinese fishermen, caused serious economic
losses, and, what is more, violated China's sovereignty.
</P>
