<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 26 (Xinhua) -- Following are the latest facts and
figures about China's foreign trade with Asia, Africa and Latin
America in January-April of 1999, provided by the General
Administration of Customs:
</P>
<P>
-- Trade volume with other countries and regions across Asia
reached 55.77 billion U.S. dollars, down 4.2 percent from the same
